dmca.title: Accel-Team Claims Infringement

From: [Sender] To: DMCA complaints User Support	Date: 20/10/02 Time: 12:49:00		Page 1 of 2

Accel Team
Advancing employee productivity
...job security depends on it!

[Private], Egremont, Cumbria, CA22 2EG, [Private], http://www.accel-team.com/



		Sunday 20 September 2002
		Google, Inc.
		Attn: User Support, DMCA complaints
		[Private]
		Mountain View, CA 94043


		Dear Sirs

					Copyright Infringement #[private]
    
		The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on the following google [sic] search string:
    
		http://www.google.com/
		search?q=+site:web.kyunghee.ac.kr+self+fulfilling+prophesy&hl=en&lr=&ie=UTF-
		8&newwindow=1&start=10=&sa=N
			This string returns 3 pages, on which the following returned links contained material
		owned by Accel-Team.com, contained in the http://www.accel-team.com/motivation/ section.
		The offending links are as follows:
    
		Page 1
    
		web.kyunghee.ac.kr/~ron/Self-fulfilling%20Phrophesy-Intro.html

From: [Sender] To: DMCA complaints User Support	Date: 20/10/02 Time: 12:49:00		Page 2 of 2




		Page 3

		web.kyunghee.ac.kr/~ron/Scientific%20Management-05.html
		web.kyunghee.ac.kr/~ron/Scientific%20Management-03.html
		web.kyunghee.ac.kr/~ron/Scientific%20Management-04.html
		web.kyunghee.ac.kr/~ron/Hawthorne%20Studies.html
    
			The above string/links returned by Google do not contain all the pages that contained
		material owned by Accel-Team.com. For example: web.kyunghee.ac.kr/~ron/
		Scientific%20Management-02.html contains material not in Google's index, but contains
		material owned by Accel-Team.com.
			As far as I am able to discern, the email address of the person whose name is (illegally/
		incorrectly) associated with this reported site appears to be Professor [Private], his
		stated email address being: [Private].
			I have a good faith belief that use of the copyrighted materials described above on the
		allegedly infringing web pages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.
			I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate
		and that I am the copyright owner or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an
		exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.
    
		Yours sincerely


		[Sender]
